data.title: Who made Against All Odds, Phil Collins or Genesis?
data.meta_description: Answer (1 of 3): “Against All Odds” was very much a PC track though it was not specifically written for the movie of the same name. Phil was asked to write a song for the movie but was on tour at the time which wasn’t conducive to his usual writing process. Phil had the track already written but ...
